quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  15,79,"A sì gbẹ́san lára wọn. Dájújájú àwọn ìlú méjèèjì ló kúkú wà lójú ọ̀nà gban̄gba (tí ẹ̀ ń tọ̀ lọ tọ̀ bọ̀)."
  15,80,"Dájúdájú àwọn ará Ihò àpáta pe àwọn Òjíṣẹ́ ní òpùrọ́."
  15,81,"A sì fún wọn ní àwọn àmì Wa. Àmọ́ wọ́n gbúnrí kúrò níbẹ̀."
  16,58,"Nígbà tí wọ́n bá fún ọ̀kan nínú wọn ní ìró ìdùnnú (pé ó bí) ọmọbìnrin, ojú rẹ̀ yóò di dúdú fún ìbànújẹ́, tí ó sì máa pa á mọ́ra."
  16,59,"Ó sì máa fi ara pamọ́ fún àwọn ènìyàn nítorí ìró aburú tí wọ́n fún un. Ṣé ó máa gbà a mú ní n̄ǹkan àbùkù ni tàbí ó máa bò ó mọ́lẹ̀ láàyè? Ẹ gbọ́, ohun tí wọ́n ń dá lẹ́jọ́ burú!"
  16,60,"Ti àwọn tí kò gbàgbọ́ nínú Ọjọ́ Ìkẹ́yìn ni àkàwé aburú. Ti Allāhu sì ni àkàwé tó ga jùlọ. Àti pé Òun ni Alágbára, Ọlọ́gbọ́n."
  17,25,"Olúwa yín nímọ̀ jùlọ nípa ohun tí ń bẹ nínú ẹ̀mí yín, tí ẹ bá jẹ́ ẹni rere. Dájúdájú Ó ń jẹ́ Aláforíjìn fún àwọn olùronúpìwàdà."
  17,26,"Fún ẹbí ní ẹ̀tọ́ rẹ̀. (Fún) mẹ̀kúnnù àti onírìn-àjò (tí agara dá ní n̄ǹkan). Kí o sì má ṣe ná dúkìá yín ní ìná-àpà."
  17,27,"Dájúdájú àwọn àpà, wọ́n jẹ́ ọmọ ìyá àwọn ṣaetọ̄n. Aláìmoore sì ni aṣ-Ṣaetọ̄n jẹ́ sí Olúwa rẹ̀."